    button.btn.btn--warning.btn--3d Warning
    button.btn.btn--success.btn--3d Success
    button.btn.btn--danger.btn--3d Danger  

  h3 Buttons with Big Text

  p Add #[code .big] for increased text and/or icon size:
  
  a.btn.btn--primary(href="#/")
    | Find out more &hellip;
  =" "
  a.btn.btn--primary.big(href="#/")
    | Find out more &hellip;
  
  h3.mt--line Small, Default and Large Buttons
  
  p Add #[code .btn--sm] for a smaller button, or #[code .btn--lg] for a larger button:

  a.btn.btn--primary.btn--sm(href="#/")
    | Small
  = " "
  a.btn.btn--primary(href="#/")
    | Default
  = " "
  a.btn.btn--primary.btn--lg(href="#/")
    | Large

  p.mt--line.mr--12.bg--green-lighten-3.p--16
    | The smaller form button size has been designed for fitting within menus and menubars. In that context, give it a margin class #[code .m--4] to position it correctly.

