  h3 Buttons with Icons

  p Icons (e.g. #[a(href="http://fontawesome.io/icons/") Font Awesome]) can be included in buttons:
  
  p
    button.btn.btn--success
      | Call to action
      =" "
      i.fas.fa-arrow-right

    button.btn.btn--secondary
      i.fas.fa-folder
      |  Archive

    button.btn.btn--primary
